weave.servlets

Class RScriptFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • weave.servlets.RScriptFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.script.ScriptEngineFactory

    public class RScriptFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.script.ScriptEngineFactory
    R implementation of ScriptEngineFactory. ScriptEngineFactory is used to describe and instantiate ScriptEngines. Each class implementing "ScriptEngine" has a corresponding factory that exposes metadata describing the engine class. The "ScriptEngineManager" uses the service provider mechanism described in the "Jar File Specification" to obtain instances of all ScriptEngineFactories available in the current ClassLoader.
